@node hist "History"

  · 10-Dec-1999
    Release V1.1
    Made the emulation line (not char)  oriented. This
    is more or less ok now. This has fixed a few visual
    faults.
    Fixed bug in graphics hold/secondary colour.
    
  · 09-Dec-1999
    Fixed bug in function key macros.
    Added cursor on/off, home character, cursor up.
    Implemented backspace properly.

  · 21-Nov-1999
    Fixed scrolling bug, and corrected version (oops).

  · 19-Nov-1999
    First Public release V1.0
@endnode
@node bugs "Bugs..."

I can guarantee that there are bugs in this viewdata emulation
library. It has been written without any real specification, and
there are still some features I haven't written/written correctly.

None of the bugs in this code should be of the crash type, just the
crap viewdata layout type. But you never know.. Use this shareware
at your own risk.
@endnode

